00251 void socket_setoptions(int socketFd )
00252 {
00253   unsigned int SbMax = (1<<30) ;  /* 1GB*/
00254 
00255 
00256   while (SbMax > 1048576 )
00257     {
00258       if ((setsockopt(socketFd, SOL_SOCKET, SO_SNDBUF, (char *)&SbMax, sizeof( SbMax ) ) < 0 ) ||
00259           (setsockopt(socketFd, SOL_SOCKET, SO_RCVBUF, (char *)&SbMax, sizeof( SbMax ) ) < 0 ) )
00260         {
00261           SbMax >>= 1; /* SbMax = SbMax/2 */
00262           continue;
00263         }
00264 
00265       break;
00266     }
00267 
00268   return;
00269 } /* socket_setoptions_ctrl */
